	"entries": [
		"Silver energy bursts out from you in a 120-foot-long, 5-foot-wide {@variantrule Line [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Line}. Each creature of your choice in the {@variantrule Line [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Line} makes a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes {@damage 3d10} Force damage and has the {@condition Prone|XPHB} condition. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage only."
